title: Barbra Streisand - One Voice [1986] DVD5
description: Barbra Streisand - One Voice [1986] DVD5 On the eve of the 1986 US Presidential elections, Barbra Streisand welcomed 500 guests to her Malibu home for her first full-length concert in 20 years. Originally planned as a fundraiser for the Democratic party, the concert was subsequently broadcast on television to great acclaim and has since raised millions for charity. The concert includes many of Streisand's best-loved songs such as 'Somewhere', 'People' and 'The Way We Were'. Also features a special guest appearance from Barry Gibb.
